cc:Work.dc:title: Differing Aportionments
cc:Work.dc:source: Derived from an image by Steven Nass illustrating gerrymandering. It has CC-Commons ShareAlike licensing.
cc:Work.dc:description: An illustration of how different ways to apportion 50 precincts into 5 discricts can yield outcomes that are quite disproportionate to the electorate or proportionate.
